Welsh AM yana jin haushi game da ka a matsayin abin wasa
Akwai damuwa a cikin wasu AMs don la'akari da cewa ya kamata a canza sunayensu zuwa MWPs (Members of the Welsh Parliament).
Ya fara ne saboda shirin sauya sunan majalisar zuwa majalisar dokokin kasar Welsh.
AMs a bangarorin siyasa daban-daban suna da damuwa cewa zai iya haifar da cin mutunci.
Kungiyar AM ta Labour ta ce 'yan ta na cikin damuwa cewa  za ta koma Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu yin kokawa a waje da Wales: A Welsh twp na nufin ɓarna, pwp na nufin ƙura.
AM Wear Wool ya ce wannan kamar dukan in fushi, cewa yana da wasu kwatancen.
Wani dan majalisa na Welsh Conservative ya ce kungiyarsa ta kasance mai "buɗe zuciya" game da canjin sunan, amma ya ce ya kasance gajeren canji ne daga MWP zuwa Wasanni.
A wannan ma'anar ana furta w na Welsh daidai da yadda ake furta u na Turanci na Yorkshire.
Hukumar Majalisar Dattijai, wadda ta tsara dokoki don canja sunan, ta ce: Shari'ar ƙarshe da kuma kowane bayani game da abin da ake kira 'Yan Majalisar Dattijai zai zama batun 'yan jam'iyyar ne.
Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba wa majalisa na Welsh izinin canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta wallafa sakamakon shawarwarin da ta yi wa jama'a da kuma manufofin da ta gano game da goyon bayan da aka samu na kiran taron kasa Majalisar dokokin kasar ta Welsh.
Game da sunan AM, Hukumar ta dogara ne akan 'yan majalisar dokokin Welsh ko WMP, amma zaɓin MWP ya sami goyon baya mafi yawa daga shawarwarin jama'a.
MAM ta ba da shawarar wasu zaɓuɓɓuka, amma gwagwarmayar cimma yarjejeniya na iya zama ciwo ga Babban Jami'in, Elin Jones, wanda ake tsammanin zai gabatar da rubutacciyar doka game da canje-canjen a cikin makonni masu zuwa.
Dokokin da za a yi wa gyare-gyare za su hada da wasu canje-canje a yadda majalisa ke aiki, ciki har da dokoki game da rushewar AMs da kuma fasahar tsarin jam'iyyar.
Za a yi zaben karshe a kan tambayar abin da za a kira su bayan an yi tawaye kan dokar.
