Mutane 832 sun mutu sanadiyyar tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Adadin wadanda suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami na Indonesia ya kai 832, in ji hukumar kula da bala'i ta kasar da safiyar Lahadi.
An ce an kama mutane da yawa a karkashin gidajen da girgizar kasa ta 7.5 ta yi sanadiyyar girgizar kasa da ta kai mita 20 a ranar Juma'a, in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho a taron manema labarai.
Birnin Palu, da ke da mutane fiye da 380,000, ya cika da tarkacen datti daga gidajen da suka rushe.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum, 32, kuma an bincika kisan kai bayan an yi wa wata mata wuka
An fara binciken kisan bayan an gano gawar wata mata a Birkenhard, Merseyside da safiyar yau.
An gano mutumin mai shekara 44 da karfe 7:55 na safe da wuka a Grayson Mews da John Street, kuma an kama wani mutum mai shekara 32 a kan binciken kisan kai.
'Yan sanda sun bukaci mutanen yankin da su fito idan suka ga ko suka ji wani abu.
Sufeto Brian O'Hagan ya ce: "Binciken na kan gaba ne amma zan nemi duk wanda ke sansanin John Street da ke Birkenhead da ya ga ko ya ji wani abu mai ban mamaki ya tuntube mu.
Ina so in nemi kowa, musamman direbobin taksi, wanda zai iya kama wani abu a kan dashcam ɗin su tuntube mu saboda suna iya samun bayanai masu mahimmanci don bincikenmu.
Mai magana da yawun 'yan sanda ya tabbatar da cewa matar da aka samu ta kasance 'yar garin Birkenhead, an same ta a cikin wani banki.
Da yamma abokai sun gaskata cewa sun san matar kuma sun zo sansanin don su tambaye ta inda aka gan ta da safe.
Yanzu haka ana gudanar da bincike a kan lamarin kuma 'yan sanda sun ce suna shirye su kai rahoton ga mataimakin wanda abin ya shafa.
Wani direban taksi da ke zaune a Grayson Mew ya yi kokarin shiga cikin gidan amma 'yan sanda sun gaya masa cewa babu wanda ya shiga ko ya fita daga gidan.
Ta yi mamaki sa'ad da ta ji abin da ya faru.
An gaya wa mazauna garin cewa ba za a sake ƙyale su ba.
