Lebron zai fara bugawa Lakers wasa a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Fans suna jiran ganin LeBron James ya fara wasa a Los Angeles Lakers.
Shugaban Lakers Luke Walton ya ce James zai shiga wasan neman kofin gasar a ranar Lahadi tsakanin Denver Nuggets da San Diego.
Amma har yanzu ba a san tsawon lokacin da za a yi wasan ba.
Ya kamata ya zama sama da ɗaya amma ba zai kai 48, wanda Walton ya ce a shafin yanar gizon Lakers daidai ne.
Mai ba da rahoto na Lakers Mike Trudell ya rubuta cewa James zai iya buga wasan ƙwallon ƙafa.
Bayan kammala gasar a farkon wannan makon, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na shirin gasar Lakers na shekara shida.
"Ba na son wasan farko a halin da nake ciki a yanzu a aikina, don yin shiri", in ji shi.
Taron zaben Trump na West Virginia. Youtube Channel
Shugaba Donald Trump ya kaddamar da wasu tarurrukan siyasa a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin jerin tarurrukan da Trump zai gudanar a cikin makonni biyar masu zuwa, tare da tsayawa a wurare da dama da suka hada da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake rike zaben goyon bayan wanda ya zaɓa a matsayin babban alkalin kotun, Trump na fatan karawa goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a lokacin da jam'iyyar Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa ikon majalisar dokoki a lokacin da za a fara zaben a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne zaben Trump na yammacin Virginia zai gudana a daren yau, kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon shi a kan layi.
An shirya taron zaben Trump na Wheeling West Virginia da karfe 7 na dare ET, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon zaben Trump na West Virginia a kan layi, a ƙasa tare da bidiyo kai tsaye a Youtube.
Trump na iya yin magana game da tattaunawar wannan makon game da dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya fara rikici saboda zargin jima'i da kuma zaben amincewa da majalisar dattijai wanda ake tsammanin zai shafe kusan mako guda yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban manufar jam'iyyun siyasa da dama shi ne su taimaki 'yan Republican da ke cikin babban zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, jam'iyyar shugaban kasa Trump ta ce zaben na mako biyar na gaba zai kasance ne don karfafa masu bayar da tallafi da kuma tallafawa, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada da kuma shawo kan ikon da suke da shi a majalisa da kuma kananan majalisai, bisa ga Reuters.
"Sanarwar majalisar dokoki na da matukar muhimmanci ga shirinsa, wanda shugaban zai ziyarci kasashe da dama kamar yadda zai iya, yayin da muke shiga lokacin siyasa", in ji mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Trump wanda ya nemi a sakaya sunansa.
