Ryder Cup 2018: Kungiyar Amurka ta nuna shekara ta gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da fatan shiga gasar cin kofin mutum a ranar Lahadi
Bayan an yi wasa sau uku, za a iya samun gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar da yamma.
Ƙarfin motsa jiki shi ne ainihin tsarin wasan da aka gano amma wanda 'yan wasa suka yarda da shi, wanda sau da yawa ya nuna irin wannan nau'i na wasan kwaikwayo.
To, ina ne za su ce iko yake yanzu?
"Sun ci maki shida kuma yanzu sun kai hudu, don haka za mu dauki hakan a matsayin karamin karfafa gwiwa, ina tsammanin", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake barin ranar.
Turai tana da fa'ida, a zahiri, maki huɗu gaba tare da goma sha biyu da ke cikin harbi.
'Yan Amurkan, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna jin cewa suna da ɗan iska a kafaɗunsu kuma suna da ƙarfafawa sosai, kuma ba aƙalla irin Spieth da Justin Thomas ba, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana, kuma kowannensu zai yi alfahari da maki uku daga cikin huɗu.
Spieth ya ji rauni tun daga lokacin da aka buga shi a kan tee har zuwa lokacin da yake tafiya kamar yadda ake so.
Anurie ya yi ta kuka yayin da yake ci gaba da wasan, yana tura kwallon da ake bukata don daidaita wasan na huɗu yayin da yake motsawa tare da Thomas tare da bugun biyu bayan buga biyu.
Irin wannan murya ta haɗu da shi a cikin wani ƙwanƙwasawa wanda ya ba su nasara a 15, irin wannan yana gaya maka cewa ya yi imanin cewa Amurkawa ba su fita daga wannan ba.
"Ya kamata ka duba ciki ka rasa wasanka", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne abin da dukan 'yan wasa suke da shi yanzu.
18 don yin alama.
'Yan wasan da suka fi Spieth da Thomas a wasan na kwana biyu sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, kuma labarin gasar Ryder Cup ba shi da wata ma'ana.
Ƙungiyar Turai mai ban mamaki da ba a tsammani ba ta kasance huɗu daga cikin huɗu ba tare da wani mummunan abu ba.
Moliwood ne kawai mahaɗin da ba a rasa ba a ranar Asabar, amma sun riga sun shirya wasan farko a ranar Asabar da safe, da kuma wasan karshe na ranar Juma'a da safe.
Wasan, da kuma yadda suke motsawa daga taron jama'a sun nuna cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su yi nasara a ranar Lahadi, wanda ba tare da wani dan wasan da ya fi dacewa ba zai iya haifar da nasara a Turai a lokacin da rana ta sauka a Le Golf National fiye da Fleetwood da Molinari.
Zai fi kyau a yi duka a lokaci ɗaya a wurare dabam dabam.
Amma, ba a riga an yi maganar Turai ba.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi wasa da Sergio Garcia a wasan kwallon kafa na yau da safe, bayan sun yi wasa tare da Alex Noren.
Ƙwallon da ya yi sau ɗaya da biyu a cikin ƙwallon tara ya jefa ɗan ƙasar Sifen da kuma Sweden cikin ramin da ba za su iya fita ba.
A ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai taimake ka ka fita daga cikin rami.
Wasan kwallon kafa na mutum biyu da na mutum hudu abin mamaki ne a kusa da kallo saboda tattaunawar da ke tsakanin wannan hanyar sadarwa, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa, shawarwarin da ba su bayar ba da kuma yadda dabarun ke canzawa nan take.
Turai ta yi nasara a matsayin tawagar har zuwa yanzu kuma ta yi nasara a ranar karshe amma wasan hudu ya nuna cewa kungiyar Amurka tana da karfin gwiwa wanda wasu, musamman ma 'yan kasar Amurka, suka yi ta kalubalantar hakan.
Turai ta ci 10-6 ta shiga gasar Ryder Cup a ranar karshe
Turai za ta shiga wasan karshe na gasar Ryder Cup da gagarumar nasara bayan da ta ci 10-6 a kan Amurka a wasan kwallon kafa guda biyu da kuma na hudu a ranar Asabar.
Wadannan biyu masu motsawa, Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci ta hanyar nasara biyu da suka doke Tiger Woods a cikin ƙoƙari, suna tafiya ta hanyar hudu a Le Golf National.
Kungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, da ke neman rike kofin da aka kwace musu a Hazeline shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta ci gaba da yin tawaye da Amurkawa a wasan kwallon kafa na mutum biyu da safe, inda suka ci 3-1 a wasan.
Amurkawa sun yi nasara sosai a wasan hudu, kuma sun ci biyu, amma ba za su iya rage yawan nasarar ba.
Jim Furyk yana bukatar maki takwas daga cikin wasanni 12 da ya yi a ranar Lahadi don ya ci kofin.
Fleetwood ta kasance sabuwar kungiyar Turai ta farko da ta ci maki hudu a jere yayin da ita da Molinari, aka lasafta su da Molliwood bayan wani mako na musamman da suka kasance biyu da suka ci maki hudu a wasannin su na farko a gasar Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon kafa guda biyu, sun yi nasara da Woods da dan wasan Amurka, Bryson Dechambeau da 5&4.
Woods, wanda ya yi kwallaye biyu a ranar Asabar ya nuna kwarewarsa a wasan da ya buga amma ya jefa kwallaye 19 daga cikin 29 a kwallon daya da biyu da kuma hudu a karo na bakwai.
Justin Rose ya huta daga wasan farko na biyu na safe, ya koma ya shiga Henrik Stenson a wasan hudu wanda ya ci Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka da 2&1 - wadanda ke matsayi na farko da na uku a duniya.
Kasashen Turai ba su samu ba, ko da a ranar da iska ta yi iska mai ƙarfi a yammacin birnin Paris.
Jordan Spieth wanda ya lashe gasar sau uku da Justin Thomas sun yi nasara da maki biyu a matsayin tutar Amurka a ranar Asabar.
Sun ci nasara mai karfi 2&1 a kan Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain a wasan kwallon kafa guda biyu kuma sun sake dawowa don cin nasara a kan Poulter da Rory Mcllroy 4&3 a wasan hudu, bayan sun ci nasara a raga biyu.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup ne ƙungiyar ta dawo daga ƙimar huɗu da aka ci nasara a cikin zagaye na ɗaya, duk da haka kamar masu riƙe da kofin, ƙungiyar Furyk kawai tana buƙatar shiga wanda ya yi nasara, wanda ya yi nasara don riƙe kofin nasara.
Bayan sun yi kwana biyu suna gudu, har ma da harin ranar Lahadi ya yi kamar sun fi su.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta iya sauke makaman ba tare da samun amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa ci gaba da takunkumin yana haifar da rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma babu yadda za a yi kasar ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliyarta a irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa wata kungiyar kasashen duniya cewa a taron su na shekara-shekara na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya Koriya ta Arewa ta yi 'yan tawaye a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman nukiliya, yada wuraren gwajin nukiliya da kuma alkawarin da ta yi na cewa ba za ta kara bunkasa makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani bayani daga U,S ba.
Idan ba mu amince da Amurka ba, ba za mu amince da tsaron kasarmu ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayi, ba za mu iya sauke makamanmu ba.
Yayin da Ri ya mayar da martani ga korafin da Koriya ta Arewa ta yi game da kin amincewar Washington da shirin kawar da makaman nukiliya wanda Koriya ta Arewa za ta amfana daga shi a matsayin wani ɓangare na shirin, jawabinsa ya kasance mai amfani saboda bai yi watsi da shirin kawar da makaman nukiliya nan da nan ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da furucin Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka mai ci da kuma shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin ganin an "sake nukiliyar yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na neman kawo karshen yakin 1950-53 na Koriya, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara zubar da makaman nukiliyarta.
Washington ta kuma yi watsi da kiran da ake yi na sassauta takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka kafa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
Amurka ta dage kan shirin kawar da makaman nukiliya kuma ta kara daukaka ta hanyar haramtacciyar hanyar cimma burinta, kuma ta kara daukaka sanarwar kawo karshen yakin.
Ganin cewa za a yi mana horo da kuma hana mu yin hakan mafarki ne kawai na waɗanda ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da ƙuntatawa yana cinye rashin amincewarmu.
Ri bai yi magana game da shirin ganawa ta biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba, wanda jami'in Amurka ya sanar a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a makon da ya gabata.
Maimakon haka ministan ya yi magana game da ganawa uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata kuma ya kara da cewa: Idan wadanda suka shiga cikin batun nukiliyar nukiliya sune Koriya ta Kudu ba Amurka ba, da a ce ba a yi wannan yarjejeniyar ba.
Ko da yake, muryar Ri ta canza sosai daga shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya yi magana da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba zai yiwu ba a yi amfani da makamai masu linzami na Koriya ta Arewa don kai hari ga babban birnin Amurka, yayin da Shugaba Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin roka" wanda ke da aikin kisa.
