'Yar majalisar dokokin Amurka Maxine Waters a ranar Asabar ta musanta zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya saka bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisa uku na Republican a shafin Wikipedia.
Dan Democrat din na Los Angeles ya jaddada cewa masu gabatar da karar 'yan kungiyar ultra-right wing ne da kuma masu amfani da shafukan yanar gizo.
"Kishi, ƙiyayya, da ƙiyayya", in ji Waters a cikin wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter.
