Wannan sakon ya bayyana a intanet a ranar Alhamis, wanda ba a san wanda ya sanya shi a kan Capitol Hill ba yayin da ake muhawara a majalisar dokoki kan zargin da ake yi wa Brett Kavanaugh wanda ya zabi shi a matsayin babban alkalin kotun koli.
