Indonesia tana tsakiyar yankin Pacific Ring of Fire, kuma tana yawan fuskantar girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsawa.
Ga wasu girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin yankin Aceh da ke Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa garuruwa 14, inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gaɓar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane ɗari da ɗari suka mutu a Tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afka kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsanani a gaɓar tekun kudu, inda mutane 700 suka mutu.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afkawa garin Padang, babban birnin yankin yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, a waje da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya lalata yankuna da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa jihar Pidie Jaya a Aceh, inda ta yi sanadiyar lalacewa da kuma rikici da kuma yawan mutanen da suka rasa rayukansu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Babu wata tsunami da ta faru a wannan lokacin, amma gidaje da suka rushe sun kashe mutane sama da 100.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, mafi yawa a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gidaje kuma ta bar wasu matafiya cikin matsala na ɗan lokaci.
Ɗan Sarah Palin Ya Yi Zargi da Laifin Wuya
An kama Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, bisa zargin cin zarafin mutum.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin mutum, kuma ya shiga cikin korafin cin zarafin mutum da kuma hana kama mutum, bisa ga rahoton da Sojojin Jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
Bisa ga rahoton 'yan sanda, sa'ad da wata budurwa ta yi ƙoƙarin kira 'yan sanda don ta kai rahoton laifin da ake zarginsa da shi, sai ta karɓi wayarta.
An kama Palin a Ginin Mat-Su, an kama ta da wata takardar kudi ta $500, wadda kTUU ta bayar.
Ya bayyana a kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya bayyana cewa shi "ba shi da laifi, a gaskiya" lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da bukatarsa, cibiyar sadarwa ta yi ta murna.
Palin tana da laifi na aji uku, wanda ke nufin za a iya tsare ta a kurkuku har shekara ɗaya ko kuma a ci tarar dala 250,000.
An tuhume shi da laifin Class B, wanda za a iya yanke masa hukuncin kwana ɗaya a kurkuku ko kuma a ci tarar dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne laifin farko da aka yi wa Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an zarge ta da cin zarafin mahaifinta, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarta, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton harin.
An yi wannan shari'ar a gaban Kotun Tsohon Soji na Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016 an tuhume shi da cin zarafin mutum, da hannu a laifin cin zarafin mutum, da kuma shan giya da kuma kashe shi dangane da lamarin.
Abokinta ta zarge shi da cewa ya yi mata duka a fuska.
Tsoffin sojan sun zargi Sarah Palin a shekarar 2016 bayan da aka danganta tashin hankalin da ɗanta ke yi da PTSD da ta fara a lokacin da take aiki a Iraki.
Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia: mutum 100 sun mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a lokacin da girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta jawo tsunami kuma ta halaka gidaje dubbai.
Wutar lantarki da sadarwa sun lalace, inda ake sa ran za a samu tashin matattu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta afka a wani yanki da ke kusa da tsakiyar Sulawesi, a gabashin babban birnin Indonesia, wato Jakarta.
Bidiyo da ke yawo a wuraren shakatawa na jama'a sun nuna lokacin da ya fadi.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin bakin teku a garin Palu bayan da tsunami ya afkawa bakin tekun.
Alƙalai na tarayya sun yanke hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a NYC
Alƙalai a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da yaƙi da ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taɓa yi ba a jihar don wani laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekara 30, da satar motocin haya na Home Depot da aikata wannan mummunan aiki a kan hanyar keke a kan babbar hanyar West Highway a Lower Manhattan, tare da kashe masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu tuka kekuna a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da cewa hukuncin kisa ya dace, alƙalai za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya ji wa mutane da dama rauni, ta hanyar sanarwar da aka bayar na neman hukuncin kisa, wanda gundumar Kudancin New York ta yi.
Za a iya yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan laifuffuka biyu.
Makon da ya biyo bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta gurfanar da Saipov kan tuhume-tuhume 22 da suka hada da tuhume-tuhume takwas na kisan kai da taimakon iska, wadanda kotun tarayya ta saba amfani da su a shari'ar da ta shafi zalunci, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma zurfin tunani", in ji alƙalai, kuma ya bayyana cewa ayyukan da Saipov ya yi don ya yi masa laifi, ba su da kyau kuma sun gurbata.
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, azabtarwa, da kuma lalata", in ji sanarwar da aka yi niyya.
Biyar cikin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar baƙi ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekara goma ke nan da aka yi shari'ar hukuncin kisa a Kudancin New York.
An samu wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes da laifin kisan kai biyu da kuma sayar da miyagun kwayoyi amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg a New York, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan laifin ƙulla makirci da ya yi wa Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Yaƙin Cacar Ƙari.
A ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953, aka kashe Rosenbergs biyu da kujerar lantarki.
Saipov, ɗan Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin tausayi a kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, kamar yadda takardun kotu suka nuna.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa ya amince da abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa abin da ya sa ya kai harin shi ne kallon bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, wanda zargin ya nuna.
Ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a asibitinsa, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan zargin da ake masa na yin fyade.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu ba da shawara kan harkokin jama'a da kuma wakilin Saipov, ya ce sun yi "abin baƙin ciki" da hukuncin.
"Muna ganin cewa shawarar da aka yanke na neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukuncin daurin rai da rai a kurkuku ba tare da samun damar samun 'yanci ba zai kara tayar da hankalin masu zanga-zanga ga duk wadanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta riga ta nemi a dakatar da hukuncin kisa.
Dan majalisar Tory ya ce ya kamata a sanya NIGEL FARAGE a kan kujerar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "taron dakarun jama'a" a yau a lokacin zanga-zangar Tory.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa su "sami zafi" daga masu shakkar Turai - yayin da daya daga cikin 'yan majalisar Theresa May ya ce ya kamata ta kasance a kan shugabancin EU.
Shugaban jam'iyyar Conservative Peter Bone ya shaida wa jama'a a Birmingham a Burtaniya cewa zai fice idan Mr Farage ya zama Shugaban Brexit.
Amma May ta yi fama da tunanin cewa sake hada 'yan majalissar da suka rabu da juna ba daidai ba ne yayin da masu goyon bayan Remain Tory suka shiga zanga-zangar da ta bambanta da dakatar da Brexit a kasar.
Shugaban ya yi ta kokarin tabbatar da yarjejeniyar Chequers a cikin tsari a yayin da ake fuskantar hare-hare daga masu goyon bayan Brexit, Remainers da EU.
Ƙungiyoyin sun nace cewa zai ci gaba da ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya tare da Brussels duk da zargi - kuma ya tilasta wa masu Eurosceptics da Labour su zabi tsakanin kunshin da kuma Amnesty.
Mista Bone ya shaida wa taron Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa yana son ya kawar da Chequers.
Ya yi kwatancen cewa ya kamata a sanya Mista Farage a matsayin memba kuma a ba shi aikin da ya dace a tsakiyar Brussels.
"Idan yana da iko, ya kamata mu fita yanzu", in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: Zan tsaya wa Brexit amma ya kamata mu jefa Chequers.
Da yake bayyana rashin amincewarsa da EU, ya ce: Ba mu yi yaƙi da duniya don ta yi biyayya ba.
Muna son kafa dokokinmu a kasarmu.
Mista Boone ya rasa shawarwari kuma ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun zaben 2016: A'a cewa 'yan Birtaniya sun canza ra'ayinsu kuma suna son su kasance ba gaskiya bane.
'Yar jam'iyyar Tory ta Brexit Andrea Jenkyns tana wajen taron, kuma ta gaya wa manema labarai: Ina kawai cewa: Firayim Minista, ka saurari mutane.
Masu yawa daga cikin jama'a ba su son Chequers, 'yan adawa ba za su iya yin takara ba, jam'iyyun siyasa da masu fafutuka ba su son shi, waɗanda ke tafiya a kan tituna kuma suna ganin an zabe mu.
Don Allah a bar Chequers kuma fara sauraron.
A jawabin da ta yi, ta ce:  Firayim Ministoci suna ajiye mukaman su ne bayan sun yi alkawari.
Mista Farage ya shaida wa taron cewa 'yan siyasa suna bukatar su samu wannan iskar idan suna son su yi watsi da shawarar da aka yanke a zaben 2016.
"Wannan yanzu lamari ne na amincewa tsakanin mu - mutane - da kuma jam'iyyarmu ta siyasa", in ji shi.
 Suna kokarin hana Brexit amma muna nan a yau don gaya musu  Ba za mu bar ku ba idan kun yi hakan
Saƙo ga jama'ar da suka yi murna: Ina so ku sa wasu daga cikin 'yan siyasa, waɗanda ke kan gaba wajen ƙin Brexit, su ga zafi.
Tare da tarin sojojin kasar da suka ba mu nasara a kan Brexit, ba za mu huta ba har sai mun sake zama Burtaniya mai 'yanci, mai cin gashin kanta, mai daraja.
A wani ɓangare kuma, 'yan Remainers sun yi tafiya daga Birmingham kafin su yi taron kuma sun yi awa biyu a cikin birnin.
An fara taron 'yan adawa da Tory da kuma masu fafutukar Brexit a karshen wannan makon.
Dan jam'iyyar Labour, Lord Adonis ya zargi 'yan Conservatives da matsalar tsaro da suka sha sakamakon zaben da aka yi a majalisar.
"Akwai mutanen da ke gaya mana cewa suna da shirye-shiryen IT da duk fasahohin da suka dace da Kanada da ƙari, don iyakoki da rashin matsala, don kasuwanci kyauta da rashin iyaka a Ireland", in ji shi.
Wannan babban ƙiyayya ne.
Babu wani abu kamar Brexit na gaskiya, ya kara da cewa.
Warren ya goyi bayan 'yan takarar shugaban kasa
'Yar majalisar dokokin Amurka Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi la'akari sosai da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben na watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa dan jam'iyyar Democrat na Massachusetts ya yi magana game da makomarsa a lokacin da ake gudanar da taro a yammacin Massachusetts ranar Asabar.
Warren, wani mai sukar shugaban kasa Donald Trump, da ke neman zaben sake zaben a watan Nuwamba ya yi adawa da Rep. Geoff Diehl na jihar GOP, wanda ya kasance abokin takarar Trump a 2016 a Massachusetts.
Ya kasance a tsakiyar zargin cewa yana da damar fadada Trump a 2020.
Taron na Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shi ne taron jama'a na 36 da aka yi a cikin tsarin majami'a tun lokacin da Trump ya hau kan mulki.
Sai wani ya tambaye ta ko tana son ta tsaya takarar shugaban ƙasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, amma hakan ya haɗa da mace a matsayin shugaban ƙasa.
Kada ka kama wani a kan LSU Sims
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge, La., sun ce a ranar Asabar an kama mutum daya da ake zargi da harbin dan wasan kwando na LSU Wayde Sims a ranar Juma'a.
Sashen 'yan sanda na Baton Rouge ya sanar da kama Dyteon Simpson, 20, da karfe 11 na safe.
Sun wallafa bidiyon harbin ne a ranar Juma'a, suna neman taimako wajen gano mutumin da aka gani a hoton.
Sims, 20, an harbe shi kuma an kashe shi a kusa da harabar Jami'ar Kudancin a safiyar Juma'a.
"Wayde Sims ya samu rauni a kan kansa, kuma ya mutu sakamakon hakan", in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul ga manema labarai a ranar Asabar, ta hanyar 247sports.
Wayde ya tsaya ya kāre abokinsa sa'ad da Simpson ya harbe shi.
An tuhumi Simpson, ya yarda cewa yana wurin, yana da makami, kuma ya yarda da harbin Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da wata matsala ba, an kai shi kurkuku a Sashen 'yan sanda na East Baton Rouge Parish.
June 6-foot-6 da ya girma a Baton Rouge, Sims ya buga wasanni 32 wanda ya fara 10 a bara kuma ya ci gaba da kimanin minti 17.4, 5.6 da 2.9 a kowane wasa.
