Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a wasan da suka yi da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun biya diyya ga rashin nasarar da suka yi a gasar Elite League a ranar Juma'a ga Belfast Giants ta hanyar cin nasarar 5-3 a wasan da suka yi a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun sami jagoranci biyu a lokacin da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier suka ci kwallaye.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun sake dawowa don su sanya mutanen cikin gida da kuma rikici kafin Dwyer ya sake dawo da rayuwar Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya sake buga wa Dundee wasa kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci kwallaye biyu.
Wannan shi ne karo na uku da kungiyar Adam Keefe ta yi rashin nasara a gasar Elite League a bana, inda suka doke Dundee da ci 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Juma'a da daddare.
Wannan shi ne karo na huɗu da 'yan wasan suka yi karawa a gasar, kuma Giants sun ci gasar uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya ci gaba da ci gaba a minti na hudu a 3:35 ta hanyar Kendall McFaull, yayin da David Rutherford ya kawo taimako yayin da Beauvillier ya kara jagora bayan minti hudu.
A lokacin da ake ci gaba da karawa, Sullivan ya dawo da 'yan wasan gidansa a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya zama mai taimakawa Cownie a 15:16.
Dwyer ya ga cewa Giants sun dauki jagorancin zuwa hutu na farko lokacin da ya zira kwallaye na biyu a daren a ƙarshen kakar wasa ta farko.
Ƙungiyar gida ta sake haɗuwa kuma Bouchard ya sake haɗa su a cikin layi tare da babbar ƙwallo a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun hada kai don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee jagorancin gasar a karshen kakar wasa ta biyu, kuma ya rufe nasarar da kwallaye biyar na tawagarsa a rabin rabin kakar wasa ta karshe.
Giants, da suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka gabata, suna gida a Milton Keynes a wasan su na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
Wani Mai Kula da Jirgin Sama Ya Mutu Domin Ya Ga Mutane Daruruwan Sun Mutu a Girgizar Kasa
An yi wa wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesia yabo bayan rasuwarsa bayan ya tabbatar da cewa jirgin saman jigilar kaya da ya kwashe daruruwan mutane ya tashi lafiya.
Fiye da mutane 800 ne suka mutu, yawancinsu ba su da rai bayan girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, ta haifar da tsunami.
Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta ci gaba da addabar yankin, inda aka kama mutane da dama a karkashin ciyawa a garin Palu.
Amma duk da cewa abokan aikinsa sun gudu domin tsira, Anthonius Gunawang Agung mai shekara 21 ya yi kasala ya bar aikinsa a kan bene na kula da jirgin sama da kuma hawa a filin jirgin saman Mutiara Sis Al Jufri na Palu.
