Turai ta ci gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Team Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta hanyar doke Team USA da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 16:5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a Paris, Faransa.
Amurka ta yi nasara sau uku a Turai, kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kambun bayan da Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din Denmark, ya kai ƙwallon da ake bukata na 14.5 don ya ci Amirka.
Shahararren dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala sosai a gasar, ya jefa kwallonsa cikin ruwa a bugun 3 don rami na 16, ya rasa gasar daga Francesco Molinari.
Molinari dan wasan Italiya ya yi nasara a duk lokacinsa, ya kasance dan wasan 1-for-4 wanda ya ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar cin kofin duniya a 1979.
Jordan Spieth na Amurka ya fadi 5 da 4 daga dan wasan Turai mafi karanci Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
