Sabunta Ruwa: An rage yawan tsuntsaye a Pinellas, Manatee, da Sarasota
Rahoton da aka fitar daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da namun daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa, ruwa mai tsafta yana raguwa a yankin Tampa Bay.
Ta hanyar FWC, ana ba da rahoton yanayin ci gaban da ke cikin ƙananan yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collies - wanda ke nuna raguwa da raguwa.
Ruwa mai gishiri ya kai nisan mil 130 daga gefen tudun Pinellas zuwa kudancin garin Lee.
Ana iya ganin wasu abubuwa a kusan kilomita 10 na gabar tekun Hillsborough County, amma a wurare kalilan da suka kai na makon da ya gabata.
